headline: Best Stock to Buy Right Now: Amazon vs. Home Depot
summary: A match-up between Amazon (NASDAQ: AMZN) and Home Depot (NYSE: HD) may seem odd at first blush, but I know from experience that it's not uncommon for me to decide between two very different places to put my money when making a financial decision.  Amazon is well known for its e-commerce platform, which has 40% of the U.S. market, compared to Walmart's 7%, but the company's handful of other services are driving much of its growth.
